#### Notifications
- set your timezone in Ally by clicking on your profile on the bottom left corner, clicking profile settings and setting time zone. This will have been set based on the timezone you were in for your first login. 
- **Global Notification setting as of 2021-06-09:** Every week on Monday at 9am in the team member's timezone. ~30 minute variance for when the Slack message is received. This is a DM to you from the Ally Slackbot. We have turned this off for Product, but Team Owners can configure their own check-in rhythm by going to Team > Team Settings > Check-in Rhythm. 
- **Create custom Notifications to yourself for certain Teams, People or the Organization:** https://help.ally.io/en/articles/3343139-follow-teams-and-user-progress
- **Add a custom notification to a slack channel:** Go to Followers > Add > Slack Channels. Go to the settings wheel to set the time/date. 
  - For slack notifications, start at 7:30 minute mark https://youtu.be/8YUMhTuvt5A

